{"tid":1528283,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警察辛苦了！每次我路過警署都會同佢地行禮！希望你地都會！","createTime":"2019-09-01T13:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T05:57:17.000Z","uid":297248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4693390c9e5d83b345f8c549656fcceaae6a791f","tid":1528283,"uid":297248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:30:05.000Z","msg":"英勇港警的行為同納綷德軍無異，每次路過警署，有警車經過，甚至乎見到佢地，都會有種莫名的感動同恐懼，把右手手掌向下並45度朝天舉起向佢地致敬！我希望唔只得我會，學得佢地嘅行為與納綷無異的你也會！Salute! <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tLtNhrg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtLtNhrg.jpg&h=e4732ec1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PddUGSW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPddUGSW.jpg&h=f6187229&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6pKkCrg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6pKkCrg.jpg&h=ffac3b8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KbgCEEC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKbgCEEC.jpg&h=6d74a21a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xGj1mSX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxGj1mSX.jpg&h=8ef284ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDcm6jC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDcm6jC.jpg&h=8978cb41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M9v4jED.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM9v4jED.jpg&h=8fc2d6d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efe8029c50b76a63c9ac6d0ca066c4ab703775ad","tid":1528283,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:30:57.000Z","msg":"但我地需要你關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[推上熱門］［92 &amp; 93］中學生為我地上前線 我地一齊聲援中學生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1527952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1527952</a><b